ABOUT

he Yoido Full Gospel Global Network (YFGN) was founded to support Rev. LEE Young-hoon's missions work abroad through 60 years of Full Gospel's missionary work through exchanges between local churches and pastors and influential Korean churches and institutions all integrated into one global network.   

By encouraging and developing a Full Gospel mentality and spiritual movement, YFGN has formed a launching pad for world missions that target non-western nations in the 21st century. It seeks to secure its role based on Pentecostal teachings offer a new direction in carrying out missions.
